{
  "stem": "21180.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we had Jewish police in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by each exit to the city was Germans and the Jewish police, because some people had permission to go out of the city for working or other things.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And German came into the-- to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had the-- the Gestapo, [NON-ENGLISH], in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they had to come in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The maximum was-- they hadn't too much power.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the little towns, like in our town, was the leader, a man-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what was his name?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, I won't [INAUDIBLE] myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was, before the-- before the war-- how do I say?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Involved with the charity.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was not so wealthy as he was in-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] how do we say?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Orphan house.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was the leader of a orphan house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I knew him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so he was a public man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Rumkowski was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Chaim Rumkowski.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was the leader of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But he couldn't do what he want.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They told him what he'd do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He do the maximum-- they put-- they bring him to-- on the end, the Germans gave him-- they call it [INAUDIBLE] letter, that if he comes to Auschwitz, they should not kill him.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He will be there separate because they want to make the city without Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Should belong to the Reich, to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This was an excuse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they brought them down to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had from the Gestapo a letter, this-- he came down with the letter.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put him immediately to crematorium with his wife.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The whole family.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't-- this was-- I was-- I came after him a day later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I heard people said the day before come the leader, because I was hidden a few days.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
